1170
01:22:27,175 --> 01:22:28,635
Atenção consumidores,

1171
01:22:28,718 --> 01:22:31,054
as lojas fecharão em 5 minutos.

1172
01:22:31,096 --> 01:22:32,806
Desejamos a todos um feliz Natal

1173
01:22:32,931 --> 01:22:36,100
e feliz hanuka.

1174
01:22:51,906 --> 01:22:54,826
Tudo bem, segure firme.

1175
01:22:58,454 --> 01:23:01,415
Beleza, vamos lá.

1176
01:23:02,416 --> 01:23:03,792
Caramba.

1177
01:23:08,922 --> 01:23:09,923
Feliz Natal.

1178
01:23:11,804 --> 01:23:13,222
Boa noite.

1179
01:23:14,515 --> 01:23:18,227
- Feliz Natal, Willie.
- Na sua bunda.

1180
01:24:17,698 --> 01:24:19,116
Ah, merda.

1181
01:24:19,859 --> 01:24:20,901
